    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Ok, the deadlock is caused by this block:\n\n```\n    if p.knownBlocks.Size() >= maxKnownBlocks {\n        p.knownBlocks.Each(func(item interface{}) bool {\n            p.knownBlocks.Remove(item)\n            return p.knownBlocks.Size() >= maxKnownBlocks\n        })\n    }\n```\n\nThe `knownBlocks` is a fatih.Set, which doesn't notice that it's already locked, so the Remove double locks it.\n",
